== Building Dove Components ==

First pull the OpenDove code with

<pre>
git clone ssh://<username>@git.opendaylight.org:29418/opendove.git
</pre>

===Building the oDMC===

From the opendove directory, simply execute:

<pre>
mvn clean install
</pre>

